dataIdInfo.idPurp: The data set consists of health catchment boundaries with names in the two provinces of Haut-Lomami and Tanganyika in the Democratic Republic of the Congo (DRC). Limitations and use constraints are provided. This layer contains the Health Areas boundaries.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
GRID3 DRC Haut-Lomami and Tanganyika Health Catchment Area Boundaries, Version 01 (Beta) data set consists of two layers: health area boundaries and health zone boundaries.

The data are available for download in shapefile or Esri file geodatabase formats packaged in zip files.

Extent: Democratic Republic of the Congo: Haut-Lomami and Tanganyika Provinces

North: -4.95721649999996

West: 23.634325162

East: 30.592749525

South: -10.12403361

Coordinate system: GCS WGS 1984
